<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Smart Food Waste Reducer</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"/>
</head>
<body class="royal-bg">
    <header class="header">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> Smart Food Waste Reducer</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home</a>
            <a href="/login"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Login</a>
            <a href="/register"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Register</a>
            <a href="/about"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> About</a>
            <a href="/contact-us"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact Us</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card" style="max-width: 900px;">
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <h1 class="title">About Us</h1>
                <h2 class="subtitle">Making a difference, one meal at a time</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-bullseye" style="color: var(--accent-gold); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Our Mission</h2>
                <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    Smart Food Waste Reducer is dedicated to combating food waste by connecting food donors with receivers in need. 
                    Our platform enables individuals and businesses to share surplus food, ensuring that perfectly good food reaches 
                    those who need it most rather than ending up in landfills.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-eye" style="color: var(--accent-gold); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Our Vision</h2>
                <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    We envision a world where food waste is eliminated and no one goes hungry. Through technology and community 
                    collaboration, we aim to create a sustainable food distribution network that benefits both the environment 
                    and society.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="panel" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-star" style="color: var(--accent-gold); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>What We Offer</h2>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                    <li>Easy-to-use platform for posting and requesting food donations</li>
                    <li>Real-time matching between donors and receivers</li>
                    <li>Analytics to track your impact on reducing food waste</li>
                    <li>Secure and safe food sharing environment</li>
                    <li>Support for both individual and organizational users</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="panel">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-heart" style="color: var(--accent-gold); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Why It Matters</h2>
                <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 1rem;">
                    Food waste is a significant global issue with environmental, social, and economic implications. 
                    By redirecting surplus food to those in need, we not only reduce waste but also address food insecurity 
                    in our communities. Every donation makes a difference.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
                <a href="/register" class="btn-primary" style="text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; width: auto; padding: 0.875rem 2rem;">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Join Us Today
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>




